window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><i>Shadows for Silence in the Forest of Hell</i> is a novella set in the Cosmere. Who names their daughter Silence, and what does it imply? What is it like to grow up with this name? The answer's built into the concept of a stout pioneer woman who ran an inn on the frontier, drawing the seediest criminals the land had to offer. Sheâ€™d then track them after they left her inn and murder them for their bounties. </p><p><i>Perfect State</i> sets God-Emperor Kairominas on a date. What happens when the most important man in the world is forced to have dinner with the most important woman in the world? </p>"; 
